Company Overview of Far East DDB Public Company Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Far East DDB Public Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, offers advertising agency and related services in Thailand and internationally. It also offers in production and public relation services. The company was founded in 1964 and is based in Bangkok, Thailand.


465/1-467 Sri Ayudhya RoadThungphayathaiRatchathewiBangkok,  10400ThailandFounded in 1964



Phone: 66 2 354 3333

Fax: 66 2 646 9551

www.fareastddb.com







Key Executives for Far East DDB Public Company Limited


Far East DDB Public Company Limited does not have any Key Executives recorded. 



Far East DDB Public Company Limited Key Developments

Far East DDB Public Company Limited, Board Meeting, Jun 22, 2017
Jun 22 17
Far East DDB Public Company Limited, Board Meeting, Jun 22, 2017. Agenda: To consider changes to audit committee.


Far East Ddb Public Company Limited Reports Audited Consolidated and Parent Company Earnings Results for the First Quarter Ended March 31, 2017
May 15 17
Far East DDB Public Company Limited reported audited consolidated and parent company earnings results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2017. For the quarter, on consolidated basis, the company reported revenue from rendering of services and commissions of THB 154,278,000, profit before income tax expense of THB 27,226,000, profit attributable to equity holders of the company of THB 18,144,000, net cash used in operating activities was THB 72,113,000, purchase of property and equipment was THB 1,434,000 compared to the revenue from rendering of services and commissions of THB 121,501,000, profit before income tax expense of THB 9,807,000, profit attributable to equity holders of the company of THB 9,437,000, net cash used in operating activities was THB 13,539,000, purchase of property and equipment was THB 793,000 for the same quarter a year ago. Basic earnings per share were THB 2.42 against THB 1.26 a year ago. 

For the quarter, on parent company basis, the company reported revenue from rendering of services and commissions of THB 50,146,000, profit before income tax expense of THB 29,452,000, profit attributable to equity holders of the company of THB 23,785,000, net cash from operating activities of THB 44,395,000, purchase of property and equipment was THB 512,000 compared to the revenue from rendering of services and commissions of THB 49,100,000, profit before income tax expense of THB 1,778,000, profit attributable to equity holders of the company of THB 1,778,000, net cash from operating activities was THB 2,293,000, purchase of property and equipment was THB 198,000 for the previous year. Basic earnings per share were THB 3.13 against THB 0.24a year ago.


Far East DDB Public Company Limited Appoints Virach & Associates Office Co., Ltd. as Auditor
Apr 27 17
Far East DDB Public Company Limited approved the appointment of Dr. Virach Aphimeteetamrong, Certified Public Accountant No. 1378 and/or Mr. Chaiyakorn Aunpitipongsa, Certified Public Accountant No. 3196 and/or Mr. Apiruk Ati-anuwat, Certified Public Accountant No. 5202 and/or Dr. Preecha Suan, Certified Public Accountant No. 6718 of Dr. Virach & Associates Office Co., Ltd., to be the auditor of company for the year 2017, at the AGM held on April 27, 2047.


