                                                Far East DDB Public Company Limited
                                             Company Snapshot
                                            









                                            
	Far East DDB Public Company Limited operates in the Advertising agencies sector.
	
	In addition to historical fundamental analyses, the complete report available to purchase compares Far East DDB Public Company Limited with three other
	advertising agencies in Asia:
		
	Branding China Group
	
		of China
		(2016
	sales of 160.37 million Chinese Renmimbi [US$23.75  million]
		of which 94%
		was Traditional Advertising),
	
	GMO Tech Inc
	
		of Japan
		(2.87 billion Japanese Yen [US$25.81  million]
		), and
	
	Guru Online Holdings Ltd
	
		which is
		
		based in Hong Kong
		(160.51 million Hong Kong Dollars [US$20.55  million]
		of which 44%
		was Social Media Management Services).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	Far East DDB Public Company Limited reported sales of 739.97 million Thai Bahts (US$22.15 million)
		for the
		
		year ending
		December of 2016.
	
		This
		
			represents
		
				a very small
			
			increase of 0.4%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were 737.35 million Thai Bahts.
	
		The sales level in 2016 was fairly close to the level five years ago: in 2011, Far East DDB Public Company Limited had sales
		of 677.53 million Thai Bahts.
	

	




 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










